# PendragonDI API Pro

Context-rich, in-app duplicate detection for Python â€” real-time, local, and secure.

## ğŸš€ Quickstart (Simple Mode)

```python
from pendragondi_api_pro import duplicate_guard

@duplicate_guard
def call_api(...):
    ...
```

## âš¡ï¸ Advanced Usage

```python
from pendragondi_api_pro import duplicate_guard_pro

@duplicate_guard_pro(window_ms=3000, capture_args=False, rate_limit_per_minute=60)
def call_api(...):
    ...
```

